Package com.eventApp.DataStructures

package com.eventApp.DataStructures
Custom data structures package for optimized data handling in CampusConnect.

This package contains specialized data structures tailored for specific use cases in the event management system. These structures provide efficient operations for common workflows.

<h3>Data Structures:</h3>
  • MyEventLL - Custom linked list for event management with navigation support
  • MyClubQueue - Queue implementation for club approval workflows
  • CircularLL - Circular linked list for cyclical data access patterns

These data structures are designed to provide optimal performance for specific domain operations while maintaining simplicity and reliability.

Since:
1.0
